    "description": "Explore a world of decaying mechanical islands as Amber and her creature companion, Monty. Your home is a last surviving village in a world covered in soot and smoke, barely touched by sunlight - but even this haven will not last forever. <br>Set out on a quest to solve a mystery surrounding recent deaths and uncover secrets and lore hidden under the soot.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792920/extras/a1b725f919c25f99ce00f19bb0dee437.poster.avif?t=1668715999\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792920/extras/a1b725f919c25f99ce00f19bb0dee437.webm?t=1668715999\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792920/extras/a1b725f919c25f99ce00f19bb0dee437.mp4?t=1668715999\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Dive into an episodic adventure in the world of postapocalyptic steampunk.<br>Experience a human story about survivors, fear and kindness.<br></li><li>Explore with Monty, your animal companion - some problems will require you to see the world through his eyes.<br></li><li>Climb your way past decaying architecture to discover hidden secrets, lore, puzzles and collectibles.<br></li><li>Meet the cast of villagers with unique personalities and aid their struggles.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792920/extras/2b14f838d7f3cf9c0e3f27d2c052607a.poster.avif?t=1668715999\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792920/extras/2b14f838d7f3cf9c0e3f27d2c052607a.webm?t=1668715999\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"ht